Class JenaOntModelMemoryWalkGenerator

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMidEdgeWalkDuplicateFreeCapability, IMidTypeWalkDuplicateFreeCapability, IMidWalkCapability, IMidWalkDuplicateFreeCapability, IMidWalkWeightedCapability, INodeWalksDuplicateFreeCapability, IRandomWalkCapability, IRandomWalkDuplicateFreeCapability, IWalkGenerationCapability, IWalkGenerator

    public class JenaOntModelMemoryWalkGenerator
extends MemoryWalkGenerator
    This class transforms a JenaOnt Model (or an RDF file) into the internal data structure of this framework for the walk generation process.

      • readDataFromFile

        public void readDataFromFile(String fileToReadFrom,
                             String format)
        Read n-triples from the given file into MemoryWalkGenerator.data.
        Parameters:
        fileToReadFrom - File from which will be read (must be any RDF file such as NT, XML etc.).
        format - Predefined values are those in Lang such as:
        • "RDF/XML"
        • "RDF/XML-ABBREV"
        • "N-TRIPLE"
        • "TURTLE"
        The default value, represented by null, is "RDF/XML".
